### GET: Alle Termine abrufen
GET http://localhost:3000/appointments
Content-Type: application/json


### GET: Termine eines bestimmten Benutzers abrufen
GET http://localhost:3000/appointments/user/1
Content-Type: application/json


### POST: Einen neuen Termin erstellen
POST http://localhost:3000/appointments
Content-Type: application/json


{
  "userId": 1,
  "date": "2025-02-15",
  "time": "15:00",
  "description": "Testbesprechung"
}


### PUT: Termin aktualisieren
PUT http://localhost:3000/appointments/1
Content-Type: application/json


{
  "date": "2025-02-16",
  "time": "16:00",
  "description": "Aktualisierte Testbesprechung"
}


